<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text"><i>Cortaderia </i>species increase fire fuel loads and fire intensity, especially in areas already altered by other non-natives with which they commonly grow. See also Lambrinos (2000).</div>
